---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import SiteNav from "../components/SiteNav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro";
import Prose from "../components/Prose.astro";

const lastUpdated = "30 April 2026";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — BetsPlug"
  description="The legal terms governing your use of BetsPlug. Educational simulation only — 18+, no financial or betting advice."
>
  <SiteNav />

  <main>
    <PageHeader
      kicker="Legal"
      title="Terms of Service"
      subtitle={`Last updated: ${lastUpdated}`}
    />

    <Prose>
      <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
      <p>
        BetsPlug ("we", "us", "our") is a Dutch service that publishes
        statistical football forecasts for educational and research
        purposes. By using our website, mobile-friendly site, or any
        BetsPlug API you ("you") agree to these Terms of Service.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Educational simulation only</h2>
      <p>
        BetsPlug is <strong>not</strong> a bookmaker, broker, or financial
        adviser. Every probability, confidence score, ROI figure, and
        "Pick of the Day" we publish is the output of a statistical model
        for educational and research purposes only. None of it
        constitutes financial, investment, or betting advice. Past model
        performance is not indicative of future results.
      </p>

      <h2>3. 18+ and responsible play</h2>
      <p>
        You must be at least 18 years old to use BetsPlug. Gambling can be
        addictive — please play responsibly and within applicable laws.
        See our <a href="/responsible-gambling">responsible-play page</a>{" "}
        for support resources.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Account and subscription</h2>
      <p>
        A Free account is available without payment. Paid plans (Silver,
        Gold, Platinum) renew automatically each billing cycle through
        Stripe until you cancel. Cancellation takes effect at the end of
        the current period — no pro-rated refunds for unused days unless
        required by applicable consumer law.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Acceptable use</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Don't scrape, mirror, or republish BetsPlug content without
          written permission.
        </li>
        <li>Don't reverse-engineer the engine or attempt to bypass tier gates.</li>
        <li>Don't share paid-tier picks publicly while your subscription is active.</li>
        <li>Don't use our API in a way that imposes unreasonable load on our infrastructure.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        All model outputs, prediction histories, accuracy aggregates, and
        UI components are © BetsPlug. Public free picks may be quoted
        with attribution. The dataset itself remains our property.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
      <p>
        BetsPlug is provided "as is". We work hard to keep the engine
        accurate but make no warranty about uptime, prediction
        correctness, or fitness for any particular purpose. Your decisions
        are your own.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, BetsPlug's total
        liability arising out of your use of the service is limited to
        the amount you paid us in the twelve months prior to the claim.
        We are not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential
        losses including (but not limited to) gambling losses.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Governing law</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms are governed by Dutch law. Disputes go before the
        competent courts of the Netherlands, except where overriding
        consumer-protection law of your country of residence applies.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may revise these Terms from time to time. Material changes
        will be notified via the dashboard or by email. Continued use
        after the effective date counts as acceptance.
      </p>

      <h2>11. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these Terms? Email <a href="mailto:hello@betsplug.com"
          >hello@betsplug.com</a>.
      </p>
    </Prose>

    <Footer />
  </main>
</Layout>
